OL,3,CHolidaymakers urged to 'never' take
OL,4,Cexcess insurance from car hire firm
OL,6,FBasic car hire insurance included in
OL,7,Frental prices is usually subject to an
OL,8,Fexcess, meaning holidaymakers could be
OL,9,Fcharged the equivalent of hundreds of
OL,10,Fpounds for issues such as fixing a
OL,11,Fpuncture or replacing a windscreen,
OL,12,Faccording to Which?.
OL,14,FTo avoid being liable for this, people
OL,15,Fcan either purchase a Super Collision
OL,16,FDamage Waiver (SCDW) from their car
OL,17,Fhire company or Excess Reimbursement
OL,18,FInsurance (ERI) from car hire brokers
OL,19,Fand insurers.
