OL,3,CHolidaymakers urged to 'never' take
OL,4,Cexcess insurance from car hire firm
OL,6,FWhich? analysed SCDW cover provided by
OL,7,Fsix major car hire businesses in
OL,8,FMalaga, Spain, this summer, and
OL,9,Fcompared it with several ERI policies.
OL,11,FOn average, for a week's cover in
OL,12,FMalaga holidaymakers are being charged
OL,13,F#177 for SCDW, while ERI costs #38
OL,14,Ffrom a broker and #23 from an insurer,
OL,15,Faccording to the research.
OL,17,FWhich? also found SCDWs are
OL,18,F"inferior", with issues such as
OL,19,Fmisfuelling or stolen keys not covered.
