OL,3,CHolidaymakers urged to 'never' take
OL,4,Cexcess insurance from car hire firm
OL,6,FRory Boland, editor of magazine Which?
OL,7,FTravel, said: "All too often hiring a
OL,8,Fcar abroad is an unnecessarily
OL,9,Fstressful experience, with travellers
OL,10,Fsometimes pressured at the rental desk
OL,11,Finto buying overpriced insurance
OL,12,Fpolicies that they don't want or need.
OL,14,F"What our research shows is that you
OL,15,Fshould never take excess insurance
OL,16,Ffrom your car hire firm, no matter how
OL,17,Fhard the sell.
OL,19,F"Buy an ERI either directly from an
OL,20,Finsurer or via your car hire broker.
